title: Grateful Dead Live at Henry J Kaiser Convention Center on 1987-11-07

Set 1

Hey Pocky Way, Jack Straw, Row Jimmy, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Dupree's Diamond Blues, Box Of Rain-> Cassidy-> Might As Well

Set 2

Uncle John's Band-> Playin' In The Band-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Black Peter-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E:Not Fade Away-> E: Knockin' On Heaven's Door, E: One More Saturday Night

Rex Benefit *Lights went on, crowd wouldn't leave.Band came back played OMSN, "We Want Phil Chant before Box
